    addAnimalsPanel

    Game

    Defines a drawing area for the Graphics class to draw items that appear.
    gameBtn
    Defines a JButton to be used by the game class.
    Landscape
    Defines a 2D Tile array with animals and the ground type both defined, as well as qualities of weather.
    MainMenu
    Defines a screen for the main menu of the game.
    Pair
    Defines a single pair of Cartesian coordinates in the form (x, y).
    Settings
    Creates a settings screen that displays interactive options for the ecosystem in the Game class.
    Slider
    Defines a JButton that visually appears like a slider with a toggle.
    Tile
    Defines a single combination of an animal and a territory.
